txn start::^_level::repeatable read::{"":"※ 参数: <br>数据库事务隔离等级，可选数据库事务隔离等级为`read uncommitted`、`read committed`、`repeatable read`、`serializable`","en":"※ Param: <br>Database transaction isolation level, the optional database transaction isolation level is `read uncommitted`, `read committed`, `repeatable read`, `serializable`"}
txn start::_isAutoErrorRollBack::true::{"":"※ 参数: <br>业务逻辑结束时，发生错误是否自动回滚事务，true:发生错误回滚，不发生错误提交，false:不发生错误回滚，发生错误提交","en":"※ Param: <br>At the end of the business logic, whether the error automatically rolls back the transaction, true: error rollback, no error submission, false: no error rollback, error submission"}
txn end::_isCommit::true::{"":"※ 参数: <br>是否提交事务，true:提交，false:回滚","en":"※ Param: <br>Whether to submit the transaction, true: submit, false: rollback"}
######Module Param######

<br><br>SQL例子: <br>&emsp;&emsp;INSERT INTO table (test_id, test_value) VALUES ('@test_id@', '@test_value@')<br>&emsp;&emsp;INSERT INTO table (test_id, test_value) VALUES ('@list>>0>>test_id@', '@list>>0>>test_value@'),('@list>>1>>test_id@', '@list>>1>>test_value@')<br>&emsp;&emsp;DELETE FROM table WHERE test_id = '@test_id@'<br>&emsp;&emsp;UPDATE table SET test_value = '@test_value@' WHERE id = '@test_id@'

<br><br>SQL例子: <br>&emsp;&emsp;SELECT * FROM table WHERE test_value = '@test_value>>key@'<br>&emsp;&emsp;SELECT * FROM table WHERE test_value like '%@test_value@%'<br>&emsp;&emsp;SELECT * FROM table ORDER BY test_id DESC<br>&emsp;&emsp;SELECT * FROM table LIMIT 3 OFFSET 2